github-integrator

Purpose:
This skill provides a PowerShell-based GitHub pull request integration for GitHub Copilot / VS Code agent skills without relying on GitHub MCP.

Supported commands:
- detect-repo
- list-open-prs
- get-pr-details
- add-pr-summary-comment
- add-pr-line-comment

Required environment variable:
- gft_ai_om_github_pat

Remote support:
- HTTPS remotes such as https://github.com/owner/repo.git
- SSH remotes such as git@github.com:owner/repo.git
- GitHub Enterprise hosts using the detected host and /api/v3 base URL

Forbidden operations:
- Merging, closing, reopening, deleting, or editing pull requests
- Editing or deleting comments
- Issue, label, reviewer, assignee, milestone, or release management
- Any write action other than PR summary comments and inline PR diff comments
